Im babysitting a 7 year old who has a ton of labels and was also just returned from foster care.  She has been throwing mega fits and will also say things like Im supid, I hate myself, etc. I just kills me to hear that and Im nto sure the best way to handle it.

I have a high spirited 8 year old and severly autistic 6 yo so Im used to the mega fits that can last hours..... the I hate myself stuff is new. I think she can sense that it bothers me so bad therefore keeps saying it .

Nicole

